License: UNKNOWN
Description: # loghandler
        
        Shortcut for setup of simultaneous stream and file handlers with custom formatting in Python logging.
        
        ```python
        import loghandler
        
        logger = loghandler.create_logger("my_logger")
        logger.info("Here's a message!")
        ```
        
